  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 24 chapters of cozy, nature-themed fun. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover over 70 hidden object scenes and minigames. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy gentle, calming music as you play. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn interesting facts about a wide variety of plants. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design and decorate your very own garden oasis.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the tranquil beauty of nature with Nature Escapes, a delightful hidden object game that invites you to explore serene, handcrafted scenes from around the world. Each chapter offers a peaceful escape into the wonders of nature, where you can unwind and discover hidden treasures in stunning, picturesque landscapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/cf5668a201b54051ab29c4d48d98ca89.poster.avif?t=1729489785\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/cf5668a201b54051ab29c4d48d98ca89.webm?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/cf5668a201b54051ab29c4d48d98ca89.mp4?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you journey through 24 calming chapters filled with over 70 hidden object scenes and minigames, you'll have the chance to create your own dream garden. Decorate it with a variety of unique plants and flowers, transforming your space into a personal haven of natural beauty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/958cf439c4b234313c0dd2521486827c.poster.avif?t=1729489785\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/958cf439c4b234313c0dd2521486827c.webm?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/958cf439c4b234313c0dd2521486827c.mp4?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy fascinating tidbits about the plants you discover and let Nature Escapes guide you through a soothing adventure that brings the outdoors inside. Perfect for nature lovers and those looking for a relaxing gaming experience, this game offers the perfect blend of exploration and creativity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/ffb47f843f89a17641313b6093d5ceda.poster.avif?t=1729489785\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/ffb47f843f89a17641313b6093d5ceda.webm?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/ffb47f843f89a17641313b6093d5ceda.mp4?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unwind and enjoy the simple pleasures of nature with Nature Escapes. Your journey to a beautiful garden and peaceful landscapes awaits!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the tranquil beauty of nature with Nature Escapes, a delightful hidden object game that invites you to explore serene, handcrafted scenes from around the world. Each chapter offers a peaceful escape into the wonders of nature, where you can unwind and discover hidden treasures in stunning, picturesque landscapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/cf5668a201b54051ab29c4d48d98ca89.poster.avif?t=1729489785\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/cf5668a201b54051ab29c4d48d98ca89.webm?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/cf5668a201b54051ab29c4d48d98ca89.mp4?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you journey through 24 calming chapters filled with over 70 hidden object scenes and minigames, you'll have the chance to create your own dream garden. Decorate it with a variety of unique plants and flowers, transforming your space into a personal haven of natural beauty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/958cf439c4b234313c0dd2521486827c.poster.avif?t=1729489785\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/958cf439c4b234313c0dd2521486827c.webm?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/958cf439c4b234313c0dd2521486827c.mp4?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy fascinating tidbits about the plants you discover and let Nature Escapes guide you through a soothing adventure that brings the outdoors inside. Perfect for nature lovers and those looking for a relaxing gaming experience, this game offers the perfect blend of exploration and creativity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/ffb47f843f89a17641313b6093d5ceda.poster.avif?t=1729489785\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/ffb47f843f89a17641313b6093d5ceda.webm?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095100/extras/ffb47f843f89a17641313b6093d5ceda.mp4?t=1729489785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unwind and enjoy the simple pleasures of nature with Nature Escapes. Your journey to a beautiful garden and peaceful landscapes awaits!</p>",
